'''羅伯特·勞倫斯·斯坦'''（'''Robert Lawrence Stine'''，{{bd|1943年|10月8日||}})，<ref name="age">{{cite web|work= Ohio Reading Road Trip|url= http://www.orrt.org/stine/|title= R.L. Stine|accessdate= 2011-02-27|archive-date= 2011-01-22|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110122030213/http://www.orrt.org/stine/|dead-url= no}}</ref> 常稱'''R·L·史坦恩'''（'''R. L. Stine'''）和'''約維亞·鮑勃·斯坦'''（'''Jovial Bob Stine'''），是一位[[猶太裔美國人|猶太裔美國]][[作家|作家]]，被稱為“兒童文學界的[[史蒂芬·金|史蒂芬·金]]”。<ref name="children's literature">{{Cite web|last= |first= |title= Emily Osment stars in 'R.L. Stine's "The Haunting Hour"|work= [[Cape_Cod_Times|Cape Cod Times]]|date= 2007-10-26|url= http://www.capecodonline.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20071026/LIFE/710260303/-1/NEWS|accessdate= 2011-02-24|deadurl= yes|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20110708114939/http://www.capecodonline.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20071026%2FLIFE%2F710260303%2F-1%2FNEWS|archivedate= 2011-07-08}}</ref> 他主要創作兒童[[恐怖小說|恐怖小說]]，以寫就暢銷書《[[雞皮疙瘩_(小說)|雞皮疙瘩系列]]》出名，這部書共有32個語言版本，截止2014年約已出版3.5億冊。

==早年==
他出生於[[俄亥俄州|俄亥俄州]][[哥倫布_(俄亥俄州)|哥倫布]]，<ref name="kidsreads">{{cite web|work= KidsReads.com|url= http://www.kidsreads.com/series/series-nightmare-author.asp|title= The Nightmare Room by R. L. Stine|accessdate= 2011-05-11|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120307182951/http://www.kidsreads.com/series/series-nightmare-author.asp|archive-date= 2012-03-07|dead-url= yes}}</ref> 父母是猶太人路易斯·斯坦（Lewis Stine）、安妮（Anne；娘家姓Feinstein），分別是運務員和家庭主婦。斯坦在俄亥俄州的[[貝克斯利_(俄亥俄州)|貝克斯利]]長大，<ref name="stine">{{cite web |url=http://rlstine.com/about/ |title=About R.L. – For book and school reports |accessdate=2011-02-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131127161436/http://rlstine.com/about/ |archivedate=2013-11-27 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.encyclopedia.com/doc/1G2-2588500217.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-04-28 |archive-date=2015-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151003101249/http://www.encyclopedia.com/doc/1G2-2588500217.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author1=Ken Gordon|title=R.L. Stine still scaring up kids’ stories|url=http://www.dispatch.com/content/stories/life_and_entertainment/2013/12/09/author-still-scaring-up-kids-stories.html|accessdate=2014-11-22|work=[[The_Columbus_Dispatch|The Columbus Dispatch]]|date=2013-12-09|archive-date=2019-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330055750/https://www.dispatch.com/content/stories/life_and_entertainment/2013/12/09/author-still-scaring-up-kids-stories.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 9歲時開始寫作。<ref name="typewriter">{{Cite web|last= MacPherson|first= Karen|title= Venture into R.L. Stine's 'HorrorLand' – if you dare!|work= [[Pittsburgh_Post-Gazette|Pittsburgh Post-Gazette]]|date= 2008-04-08|url= http://www.post-gazette.com/pg/08099/871281-42.stm|accessdate= 2011-02-27|archive-date= 2011-06-28|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110628183237/http://www.post-gazette.com/pg/08099/871281-42.stm|dead-url= no}}</ref> 1965年在[[俄亥俄州立大學|俄亥俄州立大學]]獲英語文學學士學位，<ref name="family">{{Cite web|last= |first= |title= 2011 Thrillermaster: R.L. Stine|work= ThrillerFest|date= |url= http://www.thrillerfest.com/about/special-guests/|accessdate= 2011-02-25|deadurl= yes|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20110717052742/http://www.thrillerfest.com/about/special-guests/|archivedate= 2011-07-17}}</ref> 在校期間連續三年擔任學校幽默雜誌《The Sundial》的編輯。<ref name="age"/> 畢業後搬到[[紐約市|紐約市]]開始作家生涯。<ref name="stine"/>

==職業生涯==
他開始以約維亞·鮑勃·斯坦（Jovial Bob Stine）為筆名寫了一些兒童幽默文學作品，并創辦了幽默雜誌《香蕉》（Bananas），1975年至1984年間出版了72期。<ref name="stine"/> 1986年寫成了第一部驚險小說《陌生約會》（Blind Date）。<ref name="blinddate">{{Cite web|last= M. Rosenberg|first= Joyce|title= Success gives bookstores Goosebumps|work= [[The_Albany_Herald|The Albany Herald]]|date= 1996-10-27|url= http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=-NBEAAAAIBAJ&sjid=1rYMAAAAIBAJ&pg=1343,5181336&dq=rl+stine+blind+date&hl=en|accessdate= 2011-02-27|archive-date= 2019-03-30|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190330054242/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=-NBEAAAAIBAJ&sjid=1rYMAAAAIBAJ&pg=1343,5181336&dq=rl+stine+blind+date&hl=en}}</ref> 後來也曾為[[尼克國際兒童頻道|尼克國際兒童頻道]]的節目《Eureeka's Castle》寫劇本。<ref>{{cite news|last=Conradt|first=Stacy|url=http://www.mentalfloss.com/blogs/archives/36998|title=The Quick 10: The Not-Very-Scary Former Jobs of 10 Very Scary People|date=2009-10-14|publisher=''[[Mental_floss|Mental floss]]''|accessdate=2012-11-11|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100312074828/http://www.mentalfloss.com/blogs/archives/36998|archivedate=2010-03-12}}</ref> 1992年開始寫作《雞皮疙瘩》，並獲得的了很大的成功。

==私生活==
1969年6月22日與簡·沃德霍恩（Jane Waldhorn）結婚。他的妻子後來成了作家、編輯，<ref name="family"/> 1983年4月1日與瓊·瓦理查（Joan Waricha）一起創辦了跳傘出版社（Parachute Press）。<ref name="business">{{Cite web|last= |first= |title= Books and entertainment kids choose for themselves.|work= [[Parachute_Press|Parachute Press]]|date= |url= http://www.parachutepublishing.com/mainpage.html|accessdate= 2011-02-25|deadurl= yes|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20110204022913/http://parachutepublishing.com/mainpage.html|archivedate= 2011-02-04}}</ref> 他們育有一子-{zh-tw:馬修;zh-hk:馬菲;zh-cn:马修;}-，1980年6月7日出生。<ref name="family"/><ref name="work">{{Cite web|last= |first= |title= Elisabeth Weinberg, Matthew Stine|work= [[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date= 2010-07-02|url= http://www.nytimes.com/2010/07/04/fashion/weddings/04WEINBERG.html|accessdate= 2011-02-25|archive-date= 2012-09-23|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120923065428/http://www.nytimes.com/2010/07/04/fashion/weddings/04WEINBERG.html|dead-url= no}}</ref>

